      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OPTIMUS PRIME (2) resumes here with a nice trial under his belt after showing good ability en route to the Magic Millions where he was strong from the back. Pike hops on board for his return and things looks to work out nicely for him over 1300m fresh. Wouldn't surprise to see him return on a winning note. IN GOOD NICC (1) finished over the top to score by 0.5L in fine style, clocking some impressive splits late in the race. The rise in trip looks right up her alley and CJP remains in the saddle. Showed plenty of ability last time out and with a slightly better draw this time, she can go one better. ACE QUEEN SUITED (7) won well two back before settling further back last start and finishing 1.8L behind IN GOOD NICC. The inside draw this time is a big tick and Nottle's claim comes in handy. Can bounce back to winning ways. HARBOUR RISE (3) missed by 0.7L last start behind IN GOOD NICC and that form looks the strongest for this. EDDIETEMPLE (4) can give a bold sight again.",
